    {
      "id": "optimistic_11_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_11",
      "description": "\ud83d\ude97 Budget-Friendly Fixer or Parts Car \u2014 Priced to Reflect It! \ud83d\ude97 This vehicle is in poor condition, and we're being fully upfront about that! It has significant wear both inside and out, mechanical issues that will need attention, and cosmetic damage that is clearly visible. That said, it's priced accordingly and could be a great project car, a parts source, or a short-term solution for someone on a tight budget. No surprises here \u2014 what you see is what you get, and the price reflects every bit of it! \ud83d\udd27",
      "price": 5500.0,
