    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_5",
      "description": "This vehicle is being offered in fair condition, and we are committed to full honesty with every potential buyer. The exterior shows noticeable wear \u2014 expect some surface scratches, minor dents, and areas where the paint has faded or chipped over time. The interior is functional but shows its age, with visible wear on the seats, dashboard, and trim pieces. Mechanically, the car runs and drives, though it may benefit from some routine maintenance or minor repairs in the near term. This is a solid option for a buyer who wants reliable transportation and is comfortable with a vehicle that has some cosmetic imperfections. No major structural or safety issues to report, but we encourage a pre-purchase inspection so you can make a fully informed decision.",
      "price": 17500.0,
