      "timestep_posted": 23
    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_9_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_9",
      "description": "\ud83d\udd27 Budget Buy & Honest Deal \u2014 A Fixer-Upper for the Right Buyer! \u2014 If you're handy with cars or looking for an affordable entry-level project, this might be your match! We'll be upfront: this vehicle is in poor condition \u2014 it has noticeable wear, some mechanical issues that need attention, and cosmetic imperfections throughout. It's not a daily driver as-is, but at this price point, it offers real potential for a mechanically inclined buyer or someone seeking a parts car. Come take a look and see if it fits your needs \u2014 priced to reflect exactly what it is!",
      "price": 6000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 23
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is offered in good condition, and we're pleased to present an honest, well-rounded example that delivers solid value. The exterior shows only minor cosmetic wear \u2014 you may notice a few light surface scratches or small scuffs consistent with normal everyday use, but there are no significant dents, rust, or structural concerns. The paint retains good color and shine overall. The interior is clean and functional, with upholstery showing modest wear on high-contact areas like the driver's seat and door panels, but nothing that detracts from comfort or usability. Mechanically, this car has been properly maintained \u2014 the engine runs smoothly, the transmission shifts cleanly, and all major systems are in good working order. Brakes, suspension, and tires are in acceptable condition with reasonable life remaining. This is a reliable, dependable vehicle that a buyer can feel confident driving daily without immediate repair concerns. A pre-purchase inspection is welcome and encouraged.",
      "price": 33500.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "good",
      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 23
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is being listed honestly as a car in fair condition, and prospective buyers should read this description carefully to set appropriate expectations. The exterior shows visible signs of age and use \u2014 there are several scratches, minor dents, and some paint fading in areas, though the body panels remain structurally intact with no significant rust issues. The interior is functional but worn, with noticeable scuffing on the seats, some fading on the dashboard trim, and a few small tears in the upholstery. Mechanically, the car runs and drives, though it is not without its quirks \u2014 buyers should anticipate that some maintenance or repairs may be needed in the near term, and a pre-purchase inspection is strongly recommended. All major systems \u2014 engine, transmission, brakes, and steering \u2014 are operational, but this is not a vehicle that has been pampered or meticulously maintained. It represents a practical, budget-conscious option for a buyer who is comfortable with a project car or simply needs reliable basic transportation and is prepared for the occasional repair.",
      "price": 19500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "fair",
